            <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
                <h3>Step One</h3>
                <p>Attend the seminar - Sat, Jan 9th from 9:30am - 12:30pm. Before we begin, you'll complete an InBody scan. You'll leave the seminar with a printed copy of our nutrition program, which further explains many of the topics discussed during the seminar.</p>

                <h3>Step Two</h3>
                <p>Begin reading the nutrition booklet. Each section in the booklet has homework assignments to complete before moving on. Also, create an account with <a href="https://www.myfitnesspal.com/">MyFitnessPal</a>  and begin food logging.</p>

                <h3>Step Three</h3>
                <p>After two weeks of food logging, you'll meet with a coach (either in person or over the phone) to discuss your goals. The coach will provide guidance and create alignment between your lifestyle and diet to help you reach your goals.</p>

                <h3>Step Four</h3>
                <p>Continue to follow your personalized nutrition plan for the next four weeks.  Then on Sat, Feb 17th you'll complete another InBody scan to see the change in body fat and lean muscle mass.</p>
